00:25:03.560 --> 00:25:04.940 align:middle line:90%
Some of them are laughing.

00:25:04.940 --> 00:25:06.950 align:middle line:90%
Some of them can't talk.

00:25:06.950 --> 00:25:10.640 align:middle line:84%
